            Despite the problems that Aimee Semple McPherson had in her lifetime, her story is one about a woman who deeply desires to do God's will. Dr. Blumhofer does an exception job in retelling the story of Aimee, taking us back to her early Canadian roots to her Evangelistic Career and then culminating in her death of accidental overdose in Los Angeles in 1944.
        














